Program: Outlook
Title: 10/11/2011
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00ldzyh
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 14 Nov 2011
Extraordinary personal stories from around the world. Today, the pleasure and pain of being an older mother. In 2008, Susan Tollefsen became Britain's oldest first time mother at the age of 57. Also, the 12 year search launched by a Chinese man to reunite a photo he bought in a market with its rightful owner. Show less